<html>
    <head>
        <title>Search</title>
        <!-- 新 Bootstrap 核心 CSS 文件 -->
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="http://cdn.bootcss.com/bootstrap/3.3.0/css/bootstrap.min.css">

        <!-- 可选的Bootstrap主题文件（一般不用引入） -->
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="http://cdn.bootcss.com/bootstrap/3.3.0/css/bootstrap-theme.min.css">

        <!-- jQuery文件。务必在bootstrap.min.js 之前引入 -->
        <script src="http://cdn.bootcss.com/jquery/1.11.1/jquery.min.js"></script>

        <!-- 最新的 Bootstrap 核心 JavaScript 文件 -->
        <script src="http://cdn.bootcss.com/bootstrap/3.3.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="span12">
    			<h1 style="color:black">银保通测试</h1>
    			<h3 style="color:blue">任务<a href="/ybt/search/">查询</a></h3>
    			{% if error %}
                    <p style="color:red;">请将信息输入完整！</p>
                {% endif%}
                {% if running %}
                    <h5 style="color:red;">当前任务正在执行，请稍后再提交！</h5>
                {% endif %}
		    </div>
	        <div class="row clearfix">
	            <div class="col-md-6 column">
                    <form enctype="multipart/form-data" class="form-horizontal" role="form" action="" method="post">{% csrf_token %}
                        <label for="inputText" class="col-sm-2 control-label">任务号</label>
    					<div class="col-sm-10">
    						<input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="任务编号" name="workNo"/>
    					</div>

                        <label for="inputText" class="col-sm-2 control-label">sheet</label>
    					<div class="col-sm-10">
    						<input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Sheet1" name="sheetName" />
    					</div>

                        <label for="inputText" class="col-sm-2 control-label">起始行</label>
    					<div class="col-sm-10">
    						<input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="1" name="startRow" />
    					</div>

                        <label for="inputText" class="col-sm-2 control-label">结束行</label>
    					<div class="col-sm-10">
    						<input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="2" name="endRow" />
    					</div>
    				
                        <label for="inputText" class="col-sm-2 control-label">输出列</label>
    					<div class="col-sm-10">
    						<input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="2" name="col" />
    					</div>
    					
    					<label for="inputText" class="col-sm-2 control-label">参数表</label>
                        <div class="col-sm-10">
                            <input type="file" class="form-control" name="excelFile">
                        </div>
                        <label for="inputText" class="col-sm-2 control-label">试算报文</label>
                        <div class="col-sm-10">
                            <input type="file" class="form-control" name="ssFile">
                        </div>
                        <label for="inputText" class="col-sm-2 control-label">承保报文</label>
                        <div class="col-sm-10">
                            <input type="file" class="form-control" name="cbFile">
                        </div>
                        
                        <label for="inputText" class="col-sm-2 control-label">银行</label>
                        <div class="col-sm-10">
                            <select class="form-control" name="bankNo">
                                <option value=""></option>
                                <option value="ccb">建设银行</option>
                                <option value="cib">兴业银行</option>
                                <option value="cmb">招商银行</option>
                                <option value="ebc">光大银行</option>
                                <option value="pbc">中国人民银行</option>
                                <option value="spdb">浦发银行</option>
                                <option value="icbc">工商银行</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
					        <div class="col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10">
						        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default btn-primary btn-block">提 交</button>
					        </div>
				        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row clearfix">
                <h3 style="color:red;">注意事项：</h3>
                <p>1.任务号、sheet页名、起始行、结束行、输出列（返回保单号填写列）、银行代码为必填项。</p>
                <p>2.参数表必须上传，且必须为.xls格式</p>
                <p>3.只上传试算报文的银行：浦发银行</p>
                <p>4.只上传承保报文的银行：招行、光大、工行</p>
                <p>5.试算承保均需上传的银行：建行、兴业、中行</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
